{
  "stem": "13981.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You will have a picture later on where you see me with Colonel Petrovski, and sometimes in the projection booth, where I had projections to do, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sometimes at the American prosecution staff table.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So wherever evidence was needed where they had it, that's where I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Often.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's see if memory [LAUGHS] last that long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, there was Goering, Hess, Kaltenbrunner, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] von Ribbentrop, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Keitel, Jodl, Donitz, Raeder, von Papen, Schacht, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Speer, Streicher, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Funk, Frank, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Baldur von Schirach.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there's still, like, five.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Uh-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the one who succeeded Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't think of-- can't think of-- this is the one that succeeded Goebbels as the propaganda minister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All right, now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As we go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A moment of satisfaction, [LAUGH] Real satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] like-- really like ordinary human beings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, just looking at them doesn't mean too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The military and the navy people were in their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Goering was in a uniform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was not complete.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other ones were dressed in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he was in the room where we worked He, he never-- he wa-- he had to go into the courtroom once, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He told me he had to go-- this guard took him there-- to swear that the evidence that he-- that was from him was true.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you had the Russians, the French, the British, and the American.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
